flowchart TB
    Client([Client<br/>web / git CLI])
    Frontend[Frontend<br/>UI + REST + GraphQL]
    Auth[Auth / Permissions]
    GitProxy[Git Proxy<br/>routes to shard]
    GitStorage[(Git Storage<br/>sharded primary + replicas)]
    Search[Search Service<br/>trigram index]
    PRs[PR / Issues Service]
    Runners[CI Runner Pool<br/>ephemeral VMs]
    MetaDB[(Repo Metadata<br/>repo to shard)]

    Client --> Frontend
    Frontend --> Auth
    Frontend --> Search
    Frontend --> PRs
    Frontend --> GitProxy
    GitProxy --> MetaDB
    GitProxy --> GitStorage
    PRs -.->|push event| Runners
    Runners --> GitStorage

